# Private Discover environment variables (copy to .env and fill in).
# .env is gitignored. Shell exports always win over values in this file.
#
# Examples:
#   cp ~/discover/.env.example ~/discover/.env
#   mkdir -p ~/.discover && cp ~/discover/.env.example ~/.discover/.env
#
# Optional: NVD API key for faster CVSS lookups during Active recon.
# Request a free key: https://nvd.nist.gov/developers/request-an-api-key
#
# NVD_API_KEY=your-key-here
#
# Locations Discover reads (in order). Each file may fill keys that are still
# empty; non-empty shell exports always win over .env values:
#   $DISCOVER/.env
#   ~/.discover/.env
